---
import Frontgallery from "../components/Frontgallery.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import "../styles/style.css";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="da">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow">
    <title>Responsive Background Image</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="layout.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.cdnfonts.com/css/marine-sikona" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/c5d83fc88a.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <Header></Header>
    <main>
        <div class="container">
            <article class="intro">
                <img id="frontpage_img" src="/images/Is_this_the_one.png" alt="Your Image" class="image">
                <div class="front_pos_text">
                    <h1 id="susse_volander_title">SUSSE VOLANDER</h1>
                    <p id="front_image_text">Velkommen til mit digitale galleri! Udforsk en verden af farver, følelser og kreativitet gennem
                        maleri, og oplev unikke værker, der vækker glæde.</p>
                    <div class="middle">
                        <button>Shop her!</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
        <article class="front_om_mig">
          <article id="middle_spacing">
            <h2 class="spacing">Om Susse</h2>
            <p class="spacing">Jeg er Susse Volander, en kunstner med et overflødighedshorn af kreativitet! Mine
                malerier er legende og
                fyldt med liv, hvor jeg elsker at udforske forskellige teknikker og materialer. Gennem mine workshops
                inviterer jeg andre til at udfolde deres kreativitet og finde inspiration i det ukendte. Sammen kan
                vi skabe et rum for fri udfoldelse og drømmende eksperimenter!
            </p>
            <button class="spacing">Læs mere</button>
          </article>
            <div class="portrait_container">
                <img id="big_flower" src="/images/flower.svg" alt="big flower">
                <img id="small_flower" src="/images/flower.svg" alt="small flower">
                <img src="/images/susse_portrait.png" alt="susse_portrait">
            </div>
        </article>
        <Frontgallery></Frontgallery>
        <article class="container">
          <div class="image-container">
            <img id="front_workshop_img" src="/images/workshop_background_front.png" alt="workshop front image">
            <div class="text-container">
              <div class="white-box">
                <h2>Mine workshops</h2>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisci elit, sed eiusmod tempor incidunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrum exercitationem ullam corporis suscipit laboriosam, nisi ut aliquid ex ea commodi consequatur. Quis aute iure reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint obcaecat cupiditat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.</p>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisci elit, sed eiusmod tempor incidunt ut!</p>
                <button>Mine workshops</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="form">
          <div>
            <h2>Workshop mailing list</h2>
            <p>Sign up og få at vide hvad den næste workshop vil være om</p>
          </div>
          <form class="email_form" name="email-form">
            <div class="input-group">
              <input class="emailform" type="email" placeholder="Please enter your email" required />
              <button class="email-icon" type="submit"><i class="fa-regular fa-envelope"></i></button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
        
    </main>
    <Footer></Footer>
</body>

</html>

<style>
    * {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

img {
  width: auto; /* Adjust the width of the image */
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover; /* Ensure the image covers the container */
}

.intro h1 {
  margin: auto;
  font-size: 45px;
}

.container {
  position: relative;
  width: 150%; /* Adjust the width of the container */
  height: 100%; /* Ensure the container covers the height of the viewport */
  overflow: hidden; /* Hide overflow */
}

.front_pos_text {
  position: absolute;
  top: 45%;
  left: 2%;
  transform: translate(-2%, -50%);
  padding: 20px; /* Adjust as needed */
  margin-left: 40px;
  margin-right: 40px;
}

#susse_volander_title, #front_image_text {
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  color:#fcfff6;
}
#front_image_text{
  max-width: 450px;
}

.middle {
  margin-top: 15px;
}
.h3_text {
  margin-top: 30px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  text-align: center;
}

#frontpage_img {
  width: 160%; /* Adjust the width of the image for mobile view */
  height: auto;
}
.spacing {
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  margin-left: 50px;
  margin-right: 50px;
}

.container {
  width: 100%; /* Set width to 100% for mobile view */
  overflow: hidden; /* Hide overflow on mobile devices */
}

.front_om_mig {
  margin-left: 20px;
  margin-right: 20px;
}

.portrait_container {
  position: relative;
  max-width: 450px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

#big_flower {
  position: absolute;
  width: 80px;
  height: auto;
  left: 68%;
  top: 5%;
}

#small_flower {
  position: absolute;
  width: 60px;
  height: auto;
  left: 0%;
  top: 80%;
}

@keyframes rock {
  0% {
    transform: rotate(-5deg);
  }
  50% {
    transform: rotate(5deg);
  }
  100% {
    transform: rotate(-5deg);
  }
}

#big_flower,
#small_flower {
  animation: rock 5s ease-in-out infinite alternate; /* Adjust the animation duration and timing function as needed */
}

.image-container {
  position: relative;
}

.text-container {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 4%;
  transform: translate(-2%, -50%);
  padding: 20px; /* Adjust as needed */
}

.white-box {
  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Optional: Add shadow effect */
}

.white-box button {
  background-color: #007bff; /* Example button color */
  color: white;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 5px;
  cursor: pointer;
  margin-top: 15px;
}

/*//////KONTAKT FORMULAR //////////*/
.form {
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: #f2f2f2;
    background-color: white;
    padding: 40px 40px;
  }
  .form p {
    padding-top: 10px;
  }

  .email_form {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 500px;
    padding-top: 20px;
  }

  .input-group {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
  }

  .emailform {
    width: calc(100% - 40px);
    padding: 10px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 5px 0px 0px 5px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .email-icon {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 40px;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #969696;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .email-icon i {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }

@media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
  #frontpage_img {
  width: 100%; /* Adjust the width of the image for mobile view */
}
.container {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%; /* Adjust the width of the container */
  height: 100%; /* Ensure the container covers the height of the viewport */
  overflow: hidden; /* Hide overflow */
}
.front_pos_text {
  top: 35%;
  left: 6%;
}
.front_om_mig {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
margin: auto 6%;
}

#middle_spacing{
  margin: auto;
}

.white-box{
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 70%;
  margin: auto;
}
.white-box h2{
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}
.form, .email_form{
text-align: center;
margin: auto;
}
}

</style>

